<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Verify Your Email</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #16a34a 0%, #3ecf8e 100%); padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;">
    <h1 style="color: white; margin: 0;">OneFlow</h1>
    <p style="color: white; margin: 10px 0 0 0;">Plan → Execute → Bill</p>
  </div>
  
  <div style="background: #f8fafc; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;">
    <h2 style="color: #0b1220;">Hi {{name}},</h2>
    
    <p>Thank you for signing up with OneFlow! To complete your registration, please verify your email address using the OTP below:</p>
    
    <div style="background: white; border: 2px dashed #16a34a; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">Your OTP Code</p>
      <h1 style="color: #16a34a; letter-spacing: 8px; margin: 0; font-size: 36px;">{{otp}}</h1>
    </div>
    
    <p style="color: #ef4444; font-size: 14px;">⏰ This OTP will expire in 10 minutes.</p>
    
    <p>If you didn't create an account with OneFlow, please ignore this email.</p>
    
    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 30px 0;">
    
    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; text-align: center;">
      © 2024 OneFlow. All rights reserved.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
